Class Date

  • java.lang.Object
    • project.two.Date
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    Date class creates date objects, and also checks if they are valid dates as well. It also accepts date objects to see if they are valid.
    Author:
    Mikita Belausau, Harpreet Randhawa
